| HistoryText             = The Japanese Beetles are creatures that exist in the realm of [[Nowhere]] outside of what is called the Victory Garden. They are the product of [[Jimmy Jankovicz (Earth-616)|Jimmy Jupiter's]] imagination. They invade the Victory Garden in order to destroy the vegetables being grown there but are constantly opposed by its defenders, swarms of crows and [[Mantis Marines (Nowhere) (Earth-616)|Mantis Marines]]. They are inspired by the [[Imperial Japan (Earth-616)|Imperial Japanese]] army.{{r|Marvel Mystery Comics Vol 1 47}}
